      <title>比特币矿商 Bitfarms 在 Exec 提起 2700 万美元诉讼后提前解雇了临时首席执行官</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/bitcoin-miner-bitfarms-bitf-fires-interim-ceo-after-27-million-lawsuit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Bitfarms Ltd. 表示，在即将卸任的临时总裁兼首席执行官对这家加密货币矿商提起诉讼，要求因违约等问题赔偿 2700 万美元的损失后，该公司已解雇了该高管。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/bitcoin-miner-bitfarms-bitf-fires-interim-ceo-after-27-million-lawsuit</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 12:00:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
